#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.67"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.67:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.67:0.2"
msgid "7. Pattakammavagga"
msgstr "7. Deeds of Substance"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: ahi (metta) suttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.67:0.3"
msgid "67. Ahirājasutta"
msgstr "67. The Snake King"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.67:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

msgctxt "an4.67:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena sāvatthiyaṃ aññataro bhikkhu ahinā daṭṭho kālaṅkato "
"hoti."
msgstr "Now, at that time a monk in Sāvatthī passed away due to a snake bite."

msgctxt "an4.67:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho sambahulā bhikkhū yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. Ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho te "
"bhikkhū bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr ""
"Then several mendicants went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, "
"and said to him:"

msgctxt "an4.67:1.4"
msgid "“idha, bhante, sāvatthiyaṃ aññataro bhikkhu ahinā daṭṭho kālaṅkato”ti."
msgstr "“Sir, a monk in Sāvatthī has passed away due to a snake bite.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: Na hi nūna → nahanūna (bj, s1, s2, km, pts1) | naha nūna (s3)
msgctxt "an4.67:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Na hi nūna so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cattāri ahirājakulāni mettena cittena "
"phari."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, that monk mustn’t have spread a mind of love to the four royal "
"snake families."

msgctxt "an4.67:2.2"
msgid ""
"Sace hi so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cattāri ahirājakulāni mettena cittena "
"phareyya, na hi so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ahinā daṭṭho kālaṃ kareyya."
msgstr "If he had, he wouldn’t have died due to a snake bite."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.67:3.1"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.67:3.2"
msgid ""
"Virūpakkhaṃ ahirājakulaṃ, erāpathaṃ ahirājakulaṃ, chabyāputtaṃ ahirājakulaṃ, "
"kaṇhāgotamakaṃ ahirājakulaṃ."
msgstr ""
"The royal snake families of Virūpakkha, Erāpatha, Chabyāputta, and "
"Kaṇhāgotamaka. …"

msgctxt "an4.67:3.3"
msgid ""
"Na hi nūna so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu imāni cattāri ahirājakulāni mettena "
"cittena phari."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.67:3.4"
msgid ""
"Sace hi so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu imāni cattāri ahirājakulāni mettena cittena "
"phareyya, na hi so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ahinā daṭṭho kālaṃ kareyya."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.67:4.1"
msgid ""
"Anujānāmi, bhikkhave, imāni cattāri ahirājakulāni mettena cittena pharituṃ "
"attaguttiyā attarakkhāya attaparittāyāti."
msgstr ""
"Mendicants, I urge you to spread a mind of love to the four royal snake "
"families, for your own safety, security, and protection."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.67:5.1"
msgid "Virūpakkhehi me mettaṃ,"
msgstr "I love the Virūpakkhas,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:5.2"
msgid "Mettaṃ erāpathehi me;"
msgstr "the Erāpathas I love,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:5.3"
msgid "Chabyāputtehi me mettaṃ,"
msgstr "I love the Chabyāputtas,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:5.4"
msgid "Mettaṃ kaṇhāgotamakehi ca."
msgstr "the Kaṇhāgotamakas I love."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.73"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an4.67:6.1"
msgid "Apādakehi me mettaṃ,"
msgstr "I love the footless creatures,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: dvipādakehi → dipādakehi (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.67:6.2"
msgid "mettaṃ dvipādakehi me;"
msgstr "the two-footed I love,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:6.3"
msgid "Catuppadehi me mettaṃ,"
msgstr "I love the four-footed,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:6.4"
msgid "mettaṃ bahuppadehi me."
msgstr "the many-footed I love."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an4.67:7.1"
msgid "Mā maṃ apādako hiṃsi,"
msgstr "May the footless not harm me!"

#. <br>
#. VAR: dvipādako → dipādako (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.67:7.2"
msgid "mā maṃ hiṃsi dvipādako;"
msgstr "May I not be harmed by the two-footed!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:7.3"
msgid "Mā maṃ catuppado hiṃsi,"
msgstr "May the four-footed not harm me!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:7.4"
msgid "mā maṃ hiṃsi bahuppado."
msgstr "May I not be harmed by the many-footed!"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an4.67:8.1"
msgid "Sabbe sattā sabbe pāṇā,"
msgstr "All sentient beings, all living things,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:8.2"
msgid "sabbe bhūtā ca kevalā;"
msgstr "all creatures, every one:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:8.3"
msgid "Sabbe bhadrāni passantu,"
msgstr "may they see only nice things,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: kañci → kiñci (s1-3, km, mr)
msgctxt "an4.67:8.4"
msgid "mā kañci pāpamāgamā."
msgstr "may bad not come to anyone."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an4.67:9.1"
msgid "Appamāṇo buddho,"
msgstr "The Buddha is immeasurable,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:9.2"
msgid "Appamāṇo dhammo;"
msgstr "the teaching is immeasurable,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:9.3"
msgid "Appamāṇo saṃgho,"
msgstr "the Saṅgha is immeasurable."

#. <br>
#. VAR: sarīsapāni → siriṃsapāni (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.67:9.4"
msgid "Pamāṇavantāni sarīsapāni."
msgstr "But limited are crawling things,"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an4.67:10.1"
msgid "Ahivicchikā satapadī,"
msgstr "snakes and scorpions, centipedes,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:10.2"
msgid "Uṇṇanābhī sarabū mūsikā;"
msgstr "spiders and lizards and mice."

#. <br>
#. VAR: rakkhā katā me parittā → kataṃ me parittaṃ (?)
msgctxt "an4.67:10.3"
msgid "Katā me rakkhā katā me parittā,"
msgstr "I’ve made this safeguard, I’ve made this protection:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:10.4"
msgid "Paṭikkamantu bhūtāni;"
msgstr "go away, creatures!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:10.5"
msgid "Sohaṃ namo bhagavato,"
msgstr "And so I revere the Blessed One,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.67:10.6"
msgid "Namo sattannaṃ sammāsambuddhānan”ti."
msgstr "I revere the seven perfectly awakened Buddhas.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.67:10.7"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
